# CASE WHEN Questions

---

## 11. Categorize orders as Expensive or Cheap

```sql id="o0gf2v"
SELECT item,
       amount,
       CASE
           WHEN amount > 1000 THEN 'Expensive'
           ELSE 'Cheap'
       END AS category
FROM Orders;
```

---

## 12. Show whether customer is Adult or Young

```sql id="6jv9gf"
SELECT first_name,
       age,
       CASE
           WHEN age >= 25 THEN 'Adult'
           ELSE 'Young'
       END AS age_group
FROM Customers;
```

