# Self Join Questions

---

## 13. Find customers from the same country

```sql id="a2z2yn"
SELECT c1.first_name,
       c2.first_name,
       c1.country
FROM Customers c1
JOIN Customers c2
ON c1.country = c2.country
AND c1.customer_id <> c2.customer_id;
```

