# EXISTS Questions

---

## 14. Find customers who placed at least one order

```sql id="5y9lh6"
SELECT *
FROM Customers c
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Orders o
    WHERE c.customer_id = o.customer_id
);
```

---

## 15. Find customers who never placed orders using NOT EXISTS

```sql id="q2t7vb"
SELECT *
FROM Customers c
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Orders o
    WHERE c.customer_id = o.customer_id
);
```

