# Window Function Questions

---

## 16. Dense rank based on order amount

```sql id="6z7n8u"
SELECT order_id,
       amount,
       DENSE_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY amount DESC) AS drnk
FROM Orders;
```

---

## 17. Running total of order amounts

```sql id="jlwm27"
SELECT order_id,
       amount,
       SUM(amount) OVER(ORDER BY order_id) AS running_total
FROM Orders;
```

---

## 18. Find highest order for each customer

```sql id="0clg4v"
SELECT customer_id,
       MAX(amount) AS highest_order
FROM Orders
GROUP BY customer_id;
```

