# Frequently Asked Interview Concepts

### 26. Difference between WHERE and HAVING

* `WHERE` filters rows before grouping
* `HAVING` filters after grouping

Example:

```sql
SELECT country, COUNT(*)
FROM Customers
GROUP BY country
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
```

---

### 27. INNER JOIN vs LEFT JOIN

* `INNER JOIN` → only matching rows
* `LEFT JOIN` → all left table rows + matching rows

---

### 28. DELETE vs DROP vs TRUNCATE

| Command  | Removes Data | Removes Table Structure |
| -------- | ------------ | ----------------------- |
| DELETE   | Yes          | No                      |
| TRUNCATE | Yes          | No                      |
| DROP     | Yes          | Yes                     |

